lead_paragraph: CJ McCollum made five 3-pointers and scored 30 points to lead the Portland Trail Blazers to a 115-107 victory over the Sacramento Kings on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: McCollum Has 30 as Trail Blazers Beat Kings 115-107
